An article by Chinese President Xi Jinping on modernization featuring harmonious coexistence between humanity and nature will be published on Wednesday. The article by Xi, also general secretary of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee and chairman of the Central Military Commission, will be published in this year's 11th issue of the Qiushi Journal, a flagship magazine of the CPC Central Committee. The article calls for efforts to promote green and low-carbon development and fight against pollution. It also stresses the importance of the improvement of the quality and stability of the ecosystem, promotion of global sustainable development and the advancement of the modernization of national governance capacity in this field.